  "body": "<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Get a server today and play with your friends! Click <a href=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/gamerpotion\">HERE</a> or below banner &amp; Use Code <strong>GAMERPOTION</strong> to get 25 off!</span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/gamerpotion\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/684/717/cbf4e971-7207-4602-bd76-b44081f9b7df.png\" alt=\"\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Origins Mod-Required-black?style=plastic\" /></a> <a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/gamerpotion\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/buy me a coffee-support-orange?style=plastic\" /></a> <a href=\"https://discord.gg/uCPfPBvsRJ\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/870825743788158986?color=blue&amp;style=plastic\" /></a> <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/GamerPotionDev\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/my other-projects-orange?style=plastic\" /></a> <a href=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/gamerpotion\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/get%20a%20server-click%20here-blue?style=plastic\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/697/293/air-chidori-banner3.png\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Awaken your Chidori and take to the skies! Born to an Avian mother and Blazeborn father, raised by the Elytrians in a small village, you have mastered the art of continuous flight and control of heat.<br />Caution: Not every Air Chidori has yet mastered the art of landing without damage..</span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><br /></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Your vanilla experience will be further enhanced thanks for the following features:-</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #99cc00;\">➕ </span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Fire Immunity</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">You are immune to all types of fire damage.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>➕ Winged</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">You have Elytra wings without needing to equip any</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>➕ Continuous Flight</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Take to the skies. Infuse your Chidori powers with Avian abilities!</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>➕ Chidori Blood</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">You have Chidori blood running through your veins which makes you emit special particles.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>➕ Volumetric Distortion</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">You have special access to a distorted universe which allows you to carry 9 more items in your volumetric bag. You can access this bag by using your load hotbar activator key (usually the X key)</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>➖ Vandal Sprint</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Flying has taken a toll on your body. Eat Adequately to be able to sprint.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>➖ Lives of the Nine Tails</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">You have 1 less heart than Humans giving you 9 hearts only.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>➖ Fresh Air</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">When sleeping, your bed needs to be at an altitude of at least 86 blocks so you can breath fresh air.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>➖ Crash Landing</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Flying too much makes you dizzy and you cannot control your landing. Expect some damage when trying to land...</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong>Check out more Chidori Origins</strong></span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/air-chidori-origin\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/697/293/air-chidori-banner3.png\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/land-chidori-origin\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/697/295/land-chidori-banner3.png\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/aqua-chidori-origin\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/697/294/aqua-chidori-banner3.png\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/dark-chidori-origin\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/697/298/dark-chidori-banner3.png\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong>Check out the full Chidori Origins Collection mod</strong></span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/chidori-origins-collection\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/697/300/chidori-collection-banner3.png\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Permission - Feel free to use in your modpacks.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Click the banner below to get your server today! or go to <a href=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/gamerpotion\">BisectHosting.com</a>&nbsp; and make sure to use the code '<strong>gamerpotion</strong>' to get your 25% off.</span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/gamerpotion\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/608/745/bisect-banner-large3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"621\" height=\"415\" /></a></p>",
